text: Oricopis flavolineatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1939. It is known from Australia.BioLib.cz - Oricopis flavolineatus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1939
